00:12:21.180 --> 00:12:24.020
U'Ren felt comfortable bringing the idea forward.
让Nick U'Ren轻松的提出自己的想法

232
00:12:25.060 --> 00:12:27.036
And Kerr not only listened,
Kerr不仅了解了他的想法

