00:12:27.060 --> 00:12:28.620
but he implemented the idea
还实施了这个想法

234
00:12:29.340 --> 00:12:30.996
and then afterwards,
并且赛后

235
00:12:31.020 --> 00:12:32.980
gave U'Ren all the credit --
还把所有的荣誉都给了助理U'Ren

236
00:12:34.340 --> 00:12:39.860
actions all consistent with Kerr's highly inclusive approach to leadership.
这些都符合Kerr高度包容性的领导方式

237
00:12:41.100 --> 00:12:43.756
In the era of "always-on" transformation,
在一个需要持续转变的时代

238
00:12:43.780 --> 00:12:47.460
organizations are always going to be transforming.
组织需要不断的进行改变

239
00:12:49.020 --> 00:12:52.260
