00:13:00.820 --> 00:13:04.660
to boldly transform our approach to transformation.
为了勇敢的转变我们对待转变的方法

244
00:13:05.740 --> 00:13:07.396
To do that,
为了达到这个目的

245
00:13:07.420 --> 00:13:10.900
we need to start putting people first.
我们需要把人放在第一位

246
00:13:11.620 --> 00:13:12.836
